   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>MH 2449, recto: (1) I, Tsomanites (2) (it is) who write to (3) Ezekiel, who owe (4) you one fourth (5) of a tremis, and I am (6) prepared to give it to you (7) in Paone, under Matthew, (8) the lashane.  I, Stephen, (9) son of Jacob, wrote this sherd.  David, son (10) of Matthew, witness.  Zebedaeus, son (11) of Moses, witness.</ab>
         </div>
